3E%20are%20more%20technical%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20a%20beginner%20or%20struggle%20with%20back%20problems%2C%20a%20leg%20press%20machine%20might%20be%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start%2C%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20choose%20to%20do%20squats%20(and%20front%20squats%20in%20particular)%20rather%20than%20use%20a%20leg%20press%20machine%2C%20you'll%20use%20your%20core%20more%2C%20engaging%20more%20of%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20machines%20can%20be%20quicker%20if%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20move%20a%20pin%20to%20change%20the%20weight%20rather%20than%20loading%20plates%20onto%20a%20barbell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20prefer%20goblet%20squats%2C%20barbell%20back%20squats%2C%20barbell%20front%20squats%2C%20or%20any%20other%20kind%20may%20depend%20on%20your%20body%2C%20fitness%20and%20strength%20levels%2C%20and%20preference%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they%20will%20all%20help%20you%20build%20lower%20body%20muscle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDeadlifts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20deadlifting%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fafdfa895d822030329028%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeadlifts%20engage%20the%20lower%20and%20upper%20body.%3Cp%3Edusanpetkovic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeadlifts%20are%20a%20great%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20squats%2C%20they%20involve%20almost%20the%20whole%20lower%20body%20but%20use%20more%20of%20the%20muscles%20on%20the%20back%20(as%20opposed%20to%20the%20front)%2C%20including%20the%20hamstrings%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftone-butt-glutes-without-lifting-heavy-weights-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglutes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lower%20back%2C%20and%20traps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20bang%20for%20your%20buck%20in%20terms%20of%20stimulating%20a%20lot%20of%20muscle%20groups%20all%20at%20once%2C%20even%20bridging%20lower%20body%20and%20upper%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20any%20deadlift%20variation%20will%20work%2C%20be%20it%20Romanian%20deadlifts%2C%20sumo%2C%20or%20single%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHip%20thrusts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20doing%20hip%20thrusts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb003f2417f97b87cdabf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBarbell%20hip%20thrusts%20use%20the%20glutes%20to%20push%20the%20weight%20upwards%20until%20the%20body%20is%20in%20a%20straight%20line%20from%20shoulders%20to%20knees.%3Cp%3EVladimir%20Sukhachev%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHip%20thrusts%20can%20be%20done%20with%20a%20barbell%2C%20dumbbell%2C%20kettlebell%2C%20or%20machine%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20level%20and%20preference.%20Again%2C%20machines%20can%20be%20a%20time-saver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhichever%20way%20you%20do%20them%2C%20hip%20thrusts%20predominantly%20work%20the%20glutes%2C%20hamstrings%2C%20quads%2C%20and%20adductors%2C%20which%20are%20muscles%20on%20the%20inner%20thighs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHip%20thrusts%20are%20neglected%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20Wilson%20said%2C%20but%20they're%20important.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20people%20have%20lower%20back%20problems%20as%20they%20get%20older%20is%20because%20of%20the%20diminishing%20of%20glute%20muscle.%20You%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20as%20they%20get%20older%2C%20they%20lose%20their%20butt%20and%20then%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20take%20that%20burden%20off%20of%20the%20lower%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELeg%20extension%20and%20leg%20curl%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221747%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20doing%20leg%20extensions.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb03a5895d822030329412%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeg%20extensions%20target%20the%20quads.%3Cp%3ERenata%20Angerami%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIsolation%20exercises%20work%20one%20main%20muscle%20group%20and%20one%20joint%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20compound%20exercises%20which%20engage%20more%20of%20the%20body%2C%20and%20are%20thus%20generally%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20although%20leg%20extensions%20and%20leg%20curls%20are%20isolation%20exercises%2C%20if%20you%20have%20time%20to%20add%20them%20in%20they%20can%20be%20a%20great%20way%20to%20stimulate%20the%20quads%20and%20hamstrings%20for%20a%20second%20time%2C%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20gyms%2C%20one%20machine%20offers%20both%20of%20these%2C%20making%20it%20quick%20to%20switch%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOne%20or%20two%20sets%20is%20enough%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20five%20exercises%20sounds%20like%20a%20lot%2C%20don't%20panic.%20%26quot%3BThe%20good%20news%20is%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20each%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20more%20sets%20do%20mean%20more%20muscle%20growth%2C%20you%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lose-fat-cutting-calories-is-a-mistake-trainer-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20couple%20of%20sets%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20any%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20do%20up%20to%20a%20limit%2C%20the%20more%20you%20grow%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20linear%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20mean%20by%20that%20is%2C%20it's%20not%20as%20though%20set%20number%20two%20gives%20you%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20muscle%20as%20set%20number%20eight%2C%20the%20first%20two%20sets%20when%20you're%20training%20a%20particular%20muscle%20group%20will%20give%20you%20the%20biggest%20bang%20for%20your%20buck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20one%20or%20two%20intense%20sets%20of%20any%20exercise%20will%20be%20plenty%20to%20st