ssinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-20-dollar-fast-food-wage-restaurant-prices-jobs-workers-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia's%20incoming%20%2420%20minimum%20wage%20for%20fast-food%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20her%20burgers%20and%20fries%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bunaffordable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKerri%20Harper-Howie%2C%20who%20owns%2021%20McDonald's%20restaurants%20in%20California%20with%20her%20sister%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fktla.com%2Fnews%2Flocal-news%2Fmcdonalds-franchisee-you-cant-raise-prices-enough-to-cover-minimum-wage-hike%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKTLA%205%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she'll%20be%20taking%20a%20profit%20hit%20from%20the%20new%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%20up%20menu%20prices%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20we're%20doing%20because%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20matter%20is%2C%20you%20can't%20raise%20prices%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20unaffordable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20cost%20savings%20that%20we%20can%20do%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20and%20other%20ways%20to%20be%20more%20efficient%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20this%20means%20less%20profitability%20for%20us%2C%20and%20we%20will%20absorb%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Harper-Howie%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20take%20less.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMinimum%20wages%20for%20fast-food%20workers%20in%20California%20are%20going%20up%20to%20%2420%20an%20hour%20from%20April%201%20%E2%80%94%2025%25%20more%20than%20the%20state's%20current%20minimum%20wage%2C%20and%20with%20the%20ability%20for%20a%20Fast%20Food%20Council%20to%20raise%20it%20by%20up%20to%203.5%25%20each%20year%2C%20depending%20on%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20its%20original%20form%2C%20which%20would%20have%20allowed%20for%20a%202023%20minimum%20wage%20of%20up%20to%20%2422%20%E2%80%94%20has%20faced%20backlash%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busine