ubmits-all-electoral-bond-details-including-unique-numbers-to-eci%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20Is%20Your%20Governor%20Doing%3F'%3A%20SC%20Slams%20R.N.%20Ravi's%20Refusal%20to%20Re-Induct%20MLA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12172053%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-12-at-5.20.18-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20criticised%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%20R.N.%20Ravi%20for%20refusing%20to%20re-induct%20lawmaker%20K.%20Ponmudi%20as%20minister%20even%20after%20the%20suspension%20of%20his%20conviction%20by%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Ftn-governor-defying-supreme-court-seriously-concerned-about-his-conduct-supreme-court-slams-governor-rn-ravi-for-refusing-to-appoint-minister-253019%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20took%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20the%20delay%2C%20and%20asked%20Attorney%20General%20for%20India%2C%20R.%20Venkataramani%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20your%20governor%20doing%3F%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20conviction%20has%20been%20stayed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Governor%20says%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20swear%20him%20in!%20We%20will%20have%20to%20make%20some%20serious%20observations.%20Please%20tell%20your%20governor%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20take%20a%20serious%20view%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20asked%20as%20to%20how%20a%20governor%20can%20say%20%E2%80%93%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20stayed%20the%20MLA%E2%80%99s%20conviction%20%E2%80%93%20that%20%E2%80%9Chis%20reinduction%20as%20a%20Minister%20will%20be%20against%20Constitutional%20Morality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20consisting%20of%20Justice%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20was%20hearing%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20the%20governor%20to%20accept%20the%20recommendation%20made%20by%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20to%20reappoint%20Ponmudi%20as%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20situation%20had%20constrained%20the%20court%20to%20express%20serious%20concern%20about%20the%20governor%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20say%20it%20out%20loud%20in%20court%20but%20you%20are%20now%20constraining%20us%20to%20say%20that%20aloud.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20way.%20He%20is%20defying%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20stressed%20that%20when%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stays%20a%20conviction%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Governor%20has%20no%20business%20to%20tell%20us%20that%20this%20does%20not%20wipe%20off%20the%20conviction%20and%20it%20is%20non-existent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20added%20that%20this%20means%20that%20those%20who%20have%20advised%20Governor%20Ravi%20have%20not%20done%20so%20%E2%80%9Ccorrectly%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20has%20sought%20time%20till%20tomorrow%2C%20March%2022%2C%20to%20respond.%20The%20court%20was%20stern%20in%20stressing%20that%20this%20deadline%20needs%20to%20be%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPast%20conflicts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20has%20had%20several%20run-ins%20with%20DMK-led%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20past.%20%3Cspan%3ERavi%20refused%20to%20read%20the%20c%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eustomary%20address%20prepared%20for%20him%20by%20the%20state%20government%20last%20month%2C%20and%20left%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20after%20abruptly%20ending%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20budget%20session%2C%20Ravi%20also%20omitted%20portions%20Ambedkar%2C%20Dravidian%20leaders%2C%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20of%20governance%20and%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20from%20his%20speech.%20This%20gesture%20was%20condemned%20by%20the%20Stalin-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20protested%20against%20Ravi%20as%20the%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CHere%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20narrative%20has%20been%20created.%20Everything%20applicable%20for%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20say%20no.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20habit.%20So%20many%20theses%20have%20been%20written%20%E2%80%93%20all%20false%20and%20poor%20fiction.%20This%20must%20be%20broken.%20Truth%20must%20prevail.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governor%20also%20objected%20to%20the%20state%20administration%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Condriya%20arasu%E2%80%9D%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20The%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711017922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F12172053%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-12-at-5.20.18-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-rn-ravi-ponmudi-tamil-nadu-governor%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20conviction%20has%20been%20stayed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20the%20Governor%20says%20he%20won't%20swear%20him%20in!%20We%20will%20have%20to%20make%20some%20serious%20observations.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-rn-ravi-ponmudi-tamil-nadu-governor%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Man%20Complained%20Of%20Chronic%20Headaches%2C%20Now%20He%20Has%2015%20Months%20To%20Live%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERicky%20Smith%2C%2039%2C%20received%20a%20devastating%20diagnosis%20of%20terminal%20cancer.%20This%20news%20comes%20after%20just%20a%20few%20months%20of%20experiencing%20headaches%20he%20initially%20attributed%20to%20work%20stress%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F03%2F20%2Flifestyle%2Fmy-partner-thought-his-bad-headaches-were-from-stress-doctors-now-say-he-has-only-months-to-live%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Smith's%20battle%20began%20in%20February%20with%20persistent%20headaches.%20Believing%20it%20was%20simply%20a%20consequence%20of%20a%20demanding%20workload%2C%20he%20didn't%20seek%20medical%20attention.%20However%2C%20after%20two%20weeks%20with%20no%20improvement%2C%20his%20partner%2C%20Katrina%20Binfield%2C%2041%2C%20urged%20him%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%20%C2%A0Ms%20Binfield%20claims%20the%20initial%20doctor's%20visit%20yielded%20no%20significant%20diagnosis%2C%20with%20advice%20to%20simply%20rest%20and%20increase%20water%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20pain%20persisted%2C%20prompting%20Ms%20Binfield%20to%20schedule%20Mr%20Smith%20for%20an%20eye%20test.%20This%20appointment%20proved%20crucial%2C%20as%20the%20eye%20doctor%20discovered%20a%20concerning%20sign%20-%20blood%20behind%20both%20of%20Mr%20Smith's%20eyes.%20This%20discovery%20led%20to%20further%20investigation%20and%20ultimately%2C%20the%20life-altering%20diagnosis%20of%20terminal%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20eye%20exam%2C%20Ricky%20was%20urgently%20referred%20to%20Maidstone%20Hospital.**%20There%2C%20a%20CT%20scan%20revealed%20a%20shocking%20discovery%20-%20a%20mass%20on%20his%20brain.%20To%20gain%20a%20clearer%20picture%2C%20doctors%20performed%20an%20MRI%20scan%2C%20which%20confirmed%20the%20worst%3A%20an%20inoperable%20butterfly%20glioblastoma.%20This%20aggressive%20brain%20cancer%20left%20Ricky%20with%20a%20fight%20for%20his%20life%2C%20with%20doctors%20estimating%20he%20has%2015%20months%20to%20live.%20%C2%A0Anxiously%20awaiting%20biopsy%20results%2C%20Mr%20Smith%20hopes%20for%20any%20available%20treatment%20options%20that%20could%20extend%20his%20precious%20time%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Binfield%2C%20a%20make-up%20artist%2C%20from%20Minster%2C%20Isle%20of%20Sheppey%2C%20Kent%2C%20told%20South%20West%20News%20Service%2C%20%26quot%3BLife%20is%20very%20up%20and%20down%20for%20us%20at%20the%20minute.%20There%20are%20days%20when%20Ricky%20can%20be%20confused%20and%20forgetful%20and%20there%20are%20days%20when%20I%20can%20see%20the%20changes%20in%20him.%20That%20is%20really%20hard%2C%20I%20am%20watching%20my%20partner%20change%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Binfield%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20started%20getting%20constant%20headaches%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks.%20We%20thought%20at%20first%20it%20may%20have%20been%20a%20virus.%20I%20was%20ill%20just%20before%20but%20his%20lasted%20longer%20than%20mine.%20He%20is%20a%20hardworking%20man%20and%20never%20takes%20time%20off%2C%20but%20he%20was%20starting%20to%20call%20in%20sick%20and%20just%20sit%20around%20the%20house.%20I%20said%20to%20him%20'Rick%20this%20isn't%20you'%20and%20'we%20need%20to%20get%20you%20looked%20at'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Binfield%20said%20that%20sharing%20the%20sad%20news%20with%20their%20children%20-%20Louie%2C%208%2C%20Karson%2C%205%2C%20and%20Arlo%2C%202%20-%20was%20very%20difficult.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArlo%20is%20too%20little%20to%20understand%2C%20but%20I%20sat%20Louie%20and%20Karson%20down%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLouie%20is%20such%20a%20sensitive%20soul%2C%20so%20I%20was%20really%20worried%20about%20him.%20He%20got%20up%2C%20gave%20me%20a%20hug%20and%20said%2C%20'Don't%20worry%2C%20mum%20-%20we%20will%20fight%20this%2C'%20%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20and%20Karson%20cried%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20been%20amazing%2C%20but%20it%20still%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20this%20is%20happening%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20friends%20set%20up%20a%20GoFundMe%20-%20titled%20%26quot%3BRicks%20army-%20Cancer%20will%20not%20win!!%26quot%3B%20-%20to%20raise%20money%20for%20Smith's%20treatment%2C%20his%2040th%20birthday%20and%20for%20a%20planned%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711017900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Farpdfjm_ricky-smith_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Smith's%20battle%20began%20in%20February%20with%20chronic%20headaches.%20He%20believed%20it%20was%20simply%20work%20stress%2C%20he%20didn't%20seek%20medical%20attention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-man-complained-of-chronic-headaches-now-he-has-15-months-to-live-5282649%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20Replaces%20MS%20Dhoni%20As%20CSK%20Captain%20Ahead%20Of%20IPL%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108591-ruturaj-gaikwad-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERuturaj%20Gaikwad%3C%2Fa%3E%20replaced%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20skipper%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20Gaikwad%20attended%20the%20captains'%20meeting%20ahead%20of%20this%20year's%20competition%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Thursday.%20MS%20Dhoni%20was%20the%20captain%20of%20CSK%20since%20the%20inaugural%20season%20of%20IPL%20and%20he%20has%20won%20the%20title%20five%20times%20-%20the%20joint-most%20by%20any%20skipper%20alongside%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20Rohit%20Sharma.%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20has%20played%20six%20ODIs%20and%2019%20T20s%20for%20India%2C%20made%20his%20CSK%20debut%20in%202020%20and%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20represent%20the%20five%20time%20IPL%20champions%20in%2052%20games.%20The%20right-handed%20opener%20had%20a%20memorable%20run%20last%20year%2C%20aggregating%20590%20runs%20in%2016%20games%20at%20an%20impressive%20strike%20rate%20of%20147.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMS%20Dhoni%20has%20handed%20over%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings'%20captaincy%20to%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20ahead%20of%20the%20start%20of%20TATA%20IPL%202024.%20Ruturaj%20has%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20since%202019%20and%20has%20played%2052%20matches%20in%20IPL%20during%20this%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20CSK%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20their%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20team%20looks%20forward%20to%20the%20upcoming%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%20has%20had%20one%20of%20the%20most%20inspiring%20journeys%20in%20sports%20history.%20From%20working%20as%20a%20ticket%20collector%20at%20a%20railway%20station%2C%20he%20transformed%20into%20India's%20biggest%20trophy%20collector%2C%20leading%20the%20team%20to%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%202007%2C%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202011%20and%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202013%20as%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%20has%20led%20CSK%20to%20five%20IPL%20titles%20in%202010%2C%202011%2C%202018%2C%202021%20and%202023.%20Dhoni%20has%20also%20led%20CSK%20to%20two%20CLT20%20titles%20in%202010%20and%202014.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20is%20not%20only%20the%20most%20successful%20captain%20in%20franchise%20cricket%20as%20well%2C%20but%20cricket%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20right-handed%20batter%20has%20played%20250%20IPL%20matches%2C%20mostly%20for%20CSK%2C%20other%20than%20a%20stint%20with%20Rising%20Pune%20Supergiant%20from%202016%20to%202017.%20In%20these%20matches%2C%20he%20has%20scored%205%2C082%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2038.79.%20He%20has%20also%20scored%2024%20half-centuries%20in%20the%20tournament.%20He%20also%20has%20142%20catches%20and%2042%20stumpings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECSK%20will%20face%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECSK%20squad%20for%20IPL%202024%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0MS%C2%A0Dhoni%C2%A0(c)%2C%20Moeen%20Ali%2C%20Deepak%20Chahar%2C%20Tushar%20Deshpande%2C%20Shivam%20Dube%2C%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%2C%20Rajvardhan%20Hangargekar%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20Ajay%20Mandal%2C%20Mukesh%20Choudhary%2C%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%2C%20Shaik%20Rasheed%2C%20Mitchell%20Santner%2C%20Simarjeet%20Singh%2C%20Nishant%20Sindhu%2C%20Prashant%20Solanki%2C%20Maheesh%20Theekshana%2C%20Rachin%20Ravindra%2C%20Shardul%20Thakur%2C%20Daryl%20Mitchell%2C%20Sameer%20Rizvi%2C%20Mustafizur%20Rahman%2C%20Avanish%20Rao%20Aravelly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711017840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fomi4e4ro_ruturaj-gaikwad-bcci_625x300_06_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fruturaj-gaikwad-replaces-ms-dhoni-as-csk-captain-ahead-of-ipl-2024-5282522%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20replaced%20MS%20Dhoni%20as%20the%20skipper%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canoni