And%20with%20increasing%20productivity%2C%20there's%20a%20better%20chance%20that%20America%20can%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20we%20talk%20about%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20productivity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20get%20a%20handle%20on%20what%20exactly%20productivity%20means.%20At%20the%20simplest%20level%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffalling-labor-productivity-company-profit-margins-stock-market-crash-recession-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabor%20productivity%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20how%20much%20output%20(widgets%2C%20meals%2C%20spreadsheet%20computation)%20one%20person%20can%20complete%20in%20an%20hour.%20But%20measuring%20just%20how%20productive%20workers%20are%20can%20be%20tricky.%20Indeed%2C%20productivity%20is%20calculated%20from%20what%20we%20know%3A%20output%20and%20hours%20worked.%20Work%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20however%2C%20helps%20break%20down%20labor%20productivity%20into%20several%20component%20parts%20to%20give%20us%20a%20sense%20of%20the%20whole%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELabor%20quality%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20more%20skilled%20or%20educated%20the%20workers%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20they%20are%20to%20be%20productive.%20If%20employees%20take%20a%20course%20on%20how%20to%20better%20perform%20a%20critical%20task%2C%20or%20if%20they%20simply%20stay%20in%20their%20jobs%20and%20learn%20the%20ropes%20better%2C%20overall%20labor%20quality%20and%20productivity%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapital%20deepening%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Businesses%20can%20invest%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-american-commercial-real-estate-construction-boom-us-economy-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20equipment%20or%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20make%20workers%20more%20productive%20%E2%80%94%20for%20instance%2C%20a%20machine%20that%20can%20quic