20Shares%20IIT-JEE%20Aspirant's%20Rigorous%20Schedule%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0IIT%20JEE%20(Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%93%20Joint%20Entrance%20Exam)%20and%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20exam%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20prestigious%20exams%20in%20India%20and%20are%20attempted%20by%20lakhs%20of%20students%20across%20the%20country%20every%20year.%20The%20exams%20deemed%20to%20be%20the%20toughest%20in%20the%20country%20demand%20strategic%20planning%2C%20focused%20dedication%2C%20and%20a%20disciplined%20approach.%20Recently%2C%20a%20user%20on%20X%20shared%20the%20rigid%20schedule%20of%20a%20friend%20preparing%20for%20the%20JEE%20(Joint%20Entrance%20Examination)%2C%20underscoring%20the%20significance%20of%20time%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20Mr.%20Rc%20on%20X%20and%20identifies%20himself%20as%20a%2016-year-old%2C%20shared%20a%20handwritten%20timetable%20of%20his%2017-year-old%20friend.%20''Schedule%20of%20a%20close%20friend%20who%20is%20preparing%20for%20JEE%2C''%20the%20caption%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20screenshot%20of%20the%20timetable%20outlined%20his%20daily%20activities%2C%20his%20sleep%20schedule%20and%20the%20time%20allocated%20to%20studies.%20The%20young%20aspirant%20gets%20up%20at%204%3A30%20am%20every%20day%2C%C2%A0after%20sleeping%20at%20midnight%2C%20getting%20just%204.5%20hours%20of%20sleep.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20goes%20into%20revising%20old%20chapters%2C%20attending%20class%2C%20and%20completing%20class%20work%20and%20notes%20with%20hardly%20any%20time%20for%20leisure%20or%20other%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20picture%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F99hd5c8o_iit-jee-aspirant-schedule_625x300_21_March_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20motivate%20himself%2C%20the%20student%20also%20wrote%20an%20inspirational%20quote%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20schedule%20that%20read%2C%20''Never%20will%20you%20have%20this%20day%20again.%20So%20make%20it%20count.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20user%20who%20shared%20the%20post%20further%20said%20that%20his%20friend%20follows%20the%20timetable%20very%20precisely%20and%20is%20''filled%20with%20determination%20to%20bring%20his%20family%20out%20of%20poverty.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20his%20post%2C%20one%20user%20said%2C%20''Too%20hectic..no%20time%20for%20physical%20activity.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''This%20looks%20good%2C%20especially%20those%20power-naps.%20Would%20request%20to%20begin%20the%20day%20with%20meditation%2Frunning%20and%20add%20any%20sports%20for%2030%20minutes%20later%20in%20the%20day.%20All%20the%20best.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''Medical%20evidence%20shows%20that%20sleeping%20less%20than%207-8%20hours%20in%20teenage%20years%20leads%20to%20poor%20memory%2C%20lower%20learning%2C%20and%20atrophied%20problem-solving%20skills%20-%20everything%20teens%20need.%20Your%20friend%20should%20sleep%20more!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''that's%20some%20insane%20discipline%20if%20he%20does%20it%20consistently.%20My%20routine%20for%20NEET%20and%20JEE%20was%20very%20indisciplined%20and%20vague.%20Altho%20I%20had%20a%20decent%20success%2C%20but%20still%20I%20wish%20I%20was%20somewhat%20disciplined%20during%20prep%20time.%20may%20be%20it%20would%20have%20reduced%20some%20unnecessary%20stress.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20exam%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20levels%3A%20JEE%20Mains%20and%20JEE%20Advanced.%20Candidates%20have%20to%20first%20qualify%20for%20JEE%20Mains%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20advanced%20level%20of%20the%20entrance%20exam%20(JEE%20Advanced).%20The%20exam%20is%20held%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20