rly%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20or%2064.7%25%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Congress%20(10.7%25)%2C%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(3.3%25)%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(3.1%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fdata-stories%2Fdata-focus%2Fparties-garnered-7726-crore-in-transparent-donations-between-2013-23%2Farticle67972138.ece%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20the%20total%20donation%20was%20made%20through%20transparent%20means%20of%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20in%202018%2C%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20that%20exceeded%20Rs%2020%2C000%20had%20to%20be%20declared%20under%20the%20political%20finance%20laws%20implemented%20in%202003%20by%20the%20Bharaitya%20Janata%20Party-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20donations%2C%20incentivised%20by%20100%25%20tax%20deductibility%2C%20saw%20a%20notable%20increase%20over%20the%20years%2C%20reaching%20Rs%201%2C247%20crore%20in%20FY20%20from%20Rs%20309%20crore%20in%20FY14.%20However%2C%20donations%20witnessed%20a%20slight%20decline%20to%20Rs%201%2C101%20crore%20in%20FY23%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorporate%20donations%20also%20play%20a%20significant%20role%2C%20with%20entities%20such%20as%20Prudent%20Electoral%20Trust%20(PET)%20emerging%20as%20leading%20contributors.%20In%20FY23%2C%20PET%20contributed%20Rs%20256%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20Rs%2090%20crore%20to%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS).%20Additionally%2C%20M%2FS%20MKJ%20Enterprises%20Limited%20disbursed%20Rs%2045%20crore%20to%20the%20INC%2C%20while%20B.G.%20Shirke%20Construction%20Technology%20PVT%20Limited%20donated%20%E2%82%B935%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20paper%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fdata-stories%2Fdata-focus%2Fparties-garnered-7726-crore-in-transparent-donations-between-2013-23%2Farticle67972138.ece%