-nation-group-1235948107%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fthailand-film-investment-nation-group-1235948107%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTraumatised%20By%20This%26quot%3B%3A%20DNA%20Tests%20Reveal%20Shocking%20Levels%20Of%20Incest%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDNA%20test%20is%20generally%20used%20to%20determine%20the%20ancestry.%20But%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20has%20revealed%20a%20disturbing%20trend%3A%20That%20incest%20is%20far%20more%20common%20in%20the%20country%20than%20many%20think.%20Widespread%20genetic%20testing%20has%20uncovered%20many%20cases%20of%20children%20born%20to%20close%20biological%20relatives%2C%20providing%20an%20unprecedented%20accounting%20of%20incest%20in%20the%20society.%20A%20research%20published%20in%20a%20psychiatry%20text%20book%20in%201975%20put%20the%20rate%20of%20children%20born%20of%20incest%20at%20one%20in%20a%20million.%20But%20recent%20studies%20have%20shown%20the%20number%20has%20reached%20one%20in%207%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20Victoria%20Hill%2C%20who%20discovered%20the%20disturbing%20truth%20through%20a%20DNA%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20started%20talking%20about%20her%20family%20tree%20with%20an%20ex-boyfriend%20at%20their%20high%20school%20reunion%20after%20she%20had%20taken%20a%20DNA%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20were%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20their%20family%20make-up%20was%20similar%2C%20so%20the%20man%20also%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20same%20test.%20Ms%20Hill%20then%20received%20a%20text%20message%20confirming%20her%20worst%20fear%20-%20she%20was%20his%20sister.%20And%20her%20father%20was%20not%20her%20biological%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20traumatised%20by%20this.%20Now%20I'm%20looking%20at%20pictures%20of%20people%20thinking%2C%20well%2C%20if%20he%20could%20be%20my%20sibling%2C%20anybody%20could%20be%20my%20sibling%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2Fus%2Ffertility-fraud-accidental-incest-invs%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Eshe%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20got%20to%20know%20that%20she%20had%20many%20more%20siblings%20that%20just%20the%20brother%20she%20grew%20up%20with%20-%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20slept%20with%20my%20half-sibling.%20I%20went%20to%20elementary%20school%20with%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%20highlighted%20her%20case%20to%20uncover%20something%20called%20an%20accidental%20incest%2C%20which%20proliferated%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cases%20emerged%20because%20some%20people%20donated%20their%20sperm%20to%20help%20women%20conceive.%20The%20story%20that%20really%20put%20fertility%20fraud%20on%20the%20national%20radar%20was%20that%20of%20Dr%20Donald%20Cline%2C%20who%20fathered%20at%20least%2090%20children%20in%20Indiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabies%20born%20as%20a%20result%20of%20incest%20are%20at%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20having%20birth%20defects%20and%20genetic%20disorders.%20These%20identities%20are%20confirmed%20by%20third%20party%20tests%20that%20look%20for%20homozygosity%2C%20or%20ROH%20for%20short%2C%20which%20reveals%20chunks%20of%20identical%20genetic%20material%20in%20the%20DNA.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711005900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7t2ps6ng_dna-test-unsplash_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftraumatised-by-this-dna-tests-reveal-shocking-levels-of-incest-in-us-5281424%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Babies%20born%20as%20a%20result%20of%20incest%20are%20at%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20having%20birth%20defects%20and%20genetic%20disorders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftraumatised-by-this-dna-tests-reveal-shocking-levels-of-incest-in-us-5281424%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftraumatised-by-this-dna-tests-reveal-shocking-levels-of-incest-in-us-5281424%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Ftraumatised-by-this-dna-tests-reveal-shocking-levels-of-incest-in-us-5281424%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'EB%20Law%20Said%20Data%20Will%20Be%20Available%20if%20Agencies%20Needed.%20So%20Why%20Doubts%20if%20SBI%20Has%20Data%3F'%3A%20Ex-EC%20Ashok%20Lavasa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fashok-lavasa.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Ashok%20Lavasa%2C%20the%20first%20Election%20Commissioner%20in%20the%20history%20of%20independent%20India%2C%20to%20have%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20role%20in%20August%202019%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20series%20of%20controversial%20actions%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20against%20him%20shortly%20after%20the%20last%20general%20elections%2C%20has%20raised%20pointed%20questions%20on%20the%20role%20of%20the%20government%20whilst%20formulating%20the%20concept%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20or%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20(EBS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElectoral%20bonds%20have%20been%20struck%20down%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20February%2C%202024%2C%20but%20not%20after%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20secured%20at%20least%20Rs%208261%20Crore%20worth%20of%20money%2C%20anonymously%2C%20from%20corporate%20donors%20and%20individuals%2C%20creating%20a%20huge%20gap%20with%20resources%20available%20with%20the%20political%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Findias-voters-deserve-a-bond-of-probity%2Farticle67973238.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELavasa%2C%20writing%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20says%20the%20most%20intriguing%20thing%20is%20that%20while%20Section%207(4)%20of%20The%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%2C%202018%2C%20says%20that%20information%20furnished%20by%20the%20buyer%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20be%20treated%20confidential%20by%20the%20authorised%20bank%20and%20shall%20not%20be%20disclosed%20to%20any%20authority%20for%20any%20purposes%2C%20except%20when%20demanded%20by%20a%20competent%20court%20or%20upon%20registration%20of%20criminal%20case%20by%20any%20law%20enforcement%20agency%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98designers%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20EBS%C2%A0%20are%20also%20saying%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20the%20bank%20could%20not%20have%20legally%20kept%20any%20record%20of%20the%20secret%20number%20on%20the%20bond%20issued%20to%20the%20purchaser%20(in%20keeping%20with%20the%20provision%20of%20anonymity%20enshrined%20in%20the%20EBS).%20If%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20it%20would%20be%20almost%20impossible%20to%20establish%20any%20link%20between%20purchaser%20and%20recipient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESBI%20must%20have%20data%2C%20as%20it%20has%20said%20it%20does%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELavasa%20is%20saying%20this%20inconsistency%20is%20critical.%20If%2C%20he%20says%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Calphanumeric%20number%20in%20the%20bond%20was%20only%20embedded%20to%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20bond%20and%20thus%20meet%20the%20audit%20requirement.%20The%20bond%20was%20akin%20to%20currency%E2%80%9D%2C%20then%20%E2%80%9Chow%20could%20SBI%2C%20when%20forced%20to%20disclosed%20to%20an%20enforcement%20agency%2C%20reveal%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20purchaser%20but%20limit%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20investigations%20only%20to%20the%20sources%20of%20funds%3F%20Does%20this%20not%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20providing%20the%20donor-political%20party%20link%2C%20thereby%20eliminating%20the%20clue%20that%20would%20be%20vital%20to%20probe%20allegations%20of%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20pertinently%20asks%2C%20%E2%80%9CDoes%20it%20mean%20that%20the%20EBS%20created%20fiction%20%E2%80%94%20of%20the%20enforceability%20of%20the%20law%20and%20the%20accountability%20of%20the%20bank%20towards%20the%20court%20and%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agency%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Also%2C%20%E2%80%9Cif%20the%20SBI%20did%20not%20maintain%20any%20record%2C%20on%20what%20basis%20did%20it%20ask%20for%20time%20to%20collate%20information%20on%20the%20bonds%20that%20would%20link%20both%20the%20parties%3F%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20too%20in%20the%20April%202019%20interim%20order%20observed%20that%20the%20information%20is%20not%20behind%20%E2%80%9Ciron%20curtains%20incapable%20of%20being%20pierced%E2%80%9D%3F%20He%20asks%20if%20SBI%20had%20not%20maintained%20information%20matching%20donor%2C%20to%20unique%20number%20and%20the%20recipient%20political%20party%2C%20how%20could%20it%20claim%20to%20have%20the%20information%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20Election%20Commissioner%20says%20that%20it%20is%20the%20SBI%20affidavit%20due%20today%20(March%2021)%20that%20will%20shed%20more%20light%20on%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20way%20forward%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELavasa%20ends%20by%20expressing%20deep%20disquiet%20with%20the%20messaging%20being%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20and%20via%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20trying%20to%20justify%20the%20massive%20funds%2C%20half%20of%20the%20anonymous%20bonds%20since%202018%20being%20reaped%20by%20them%2C%20as%20being%20justified%20due%20to%20having%20more%20MPs.%20Lavasa%20thought%20does%20not%20name%20the%20BJP%20when%20he%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhere%20are%20we%20headed%20with%20a%20public%20debate%20where%20the%20gravity%20of%20an%20offence%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20determined%20by%20per%20capita%20crime%3F%20Why%20are%20political%20parties%20not%20determined%20to%20accept%20clean%20money%2C%20and%20not%20funds%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfurtively%20slipped%20under%20the%20door%E2%80%9D%3F%20Will%20political%20parties%20keep%20holding%20up%20the%20mirror%20to%20each%20other%20and%20leave%20people%20blinded%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20definition%20of%20itself%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98party%20with%20a%20difference%E2%80%99%20too%20gets%20knocked.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20crave%20for%20political%20parties%20with%20a%20difference%20but%20not%20those%20so%20different%20that%20they%20look%20alike.%20How%20long%20can%20we%20accept%20the%20specious%20explanation%20that%20people%20get%20the%20government%20that%20they%20deserve%3F%20I%20think%20voters%20deserve%20better.%20They%20deserve%20a%20bond%20of%20probity%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20Arun%20Goel%20suddenly%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20position%2C%20coincidentally%2C%20hours%20before%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20to%20hear%20a%20matter%20involving%20Electoral%20Bonds.%20The%20reasons%20for%20his%20sudden%20departure%20and%20not%20known.%20Lavasa%20and%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20departures%20both%20took%20place%20in%20the%20second%20tenure%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELavasa%20was%20the%20only%20member%20of%20the%20three-man%20Election%20Commission%20who%20had%20rule%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20violated%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%202019%20general%20election.%20He%20was%20selected%20as%20a%20potential%20candidate%20for%20surveillance%20just%20weeks%20after%20his%20dissent%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpegasus-project-ashok-lavasa-narendra-modi-amit-shah-model-code-of-conduct%5C%22%3Eworldwide%20%E2%80%98Pegasus%E2%80%99%20spyware%20revelations%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711005434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fashok-lavasa.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Felectoral-bond-law-ashok-lavasa-sbi-data%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20EC%20asks%2C%20'Does%20it%20mean%20that%20the%20EBS%20%5Belectoral%20bond%20scheme%5D%20created%20fiction%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20enforceability%20of%20the%20law%20and%20the%20accountability%20of%20the%20bank%20towards%20the%20court%20and%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agency%3F'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Felectoral-bond-law-ashok-lavasa-sbi-data%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Zomato%20rolled%20back%20Green%20uniform%20for%20%26quot%3BPure%20Veg%20Mode%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711005399000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108666743%2Cimgsize-882005.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fsocial%2Fexplained-why-zomato-rolled-back-green-uniform-for-pure-veg-mode-delivery-partners-in-less-than-24-hours%2Farticleshow%2F108666761.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zomato%20launched%20'Pure%20Veg%20Mode'%20nationwide%20to%20cater%20to%20India's%20vegetarian%20population.%20The%20feature%20curates%20veg-only%20restaurants%20and%20introduced%20a%20'Pure%20Veg%20Fleet'%20for%20delivery.%20However%2C%20backlash%20led%20to%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20green%20uniform%20for%20the%20vegetarian%20fleet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fsocial%2Fexplained-why-zomato-rolled-back-green-uniform-for-pure-veg-mode-delivery-partners-in-less-than-24-hours%2Farticleshow%2F108666761.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%2