pe%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPart%2011%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20series%20of%20articles%2C%20I%20aimed%20to%20provide%20some%20context%20around%20our%20environmental%20predicament%2C%20including%20climate%20change.%20I%20discussed%20its%20multilayered%20complexities%2C%20how%20we%20got%20here%2C%20and%20where%20hope%20for%20the%20future%20of%20humankind%20may%20be%20found.%20In%20this%20final%20article%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20consider%20the%20next%20hardest%20question%20I%E2%80%99m%20frequently%20asked%3A%20What%20can%20%3Cem%3EI%3C%2Fem%3E%20do%20about%20climate%20change%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20pressing%20question.%20The%20role%20of%20the%20individual%20within%20larger%20systemic%20changes%20is%20difficult%20to%20map%2C%20but%20clearly%20most%20vital.%20For%20though%20we%20are%20in%20so%20many%20ways%20enmeshed%20and%20often%20powerless%2C%20still%20the%20totality%20of%20our%20enmeshed%2C%20individual%20actions%20is%20what%20makes%20our%20world.%20Nor%20can%20our%20answers%20today%2C%20arrived%20at%20within%20our%20current%20social%20and%20material%20frameworks%2C%20be%20complete%3B%20they%20can%20only%20be%20steps%2C%20taking%20us%20into%20a%20future%20of%20inevitable%20discontinuities%3A%20unexpected%2C%20abrupt%2C%20and%20snowballing%20social%20and%20material%20changes%20stretching%20through%20our%20lifetimes%20and%20for%20generations%20beyond.%20We%20already%20live%20in%20a%20climatically%20different%20world%20than%20the%20one%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fbecoming-human-shaped-by-ice%5C%22%3Eshaped%20human%20evolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20all%20of%20human%20history%E2%80%94the%20world%20to%20which%20we%20are%20best%20adapted%E2%80%94and%20more%20extreme%20changes%20are%20inevitable.%20For%20both%20the%20Earth-system%20and%20its%20subordinate%20human%20system%20have%20a%20momentum%20that%20carries%20us%20along%20and%20is%20difficult%20to%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20rather%20than%20imagine%20that%20any%20individual%20can%20do%20something%20to%20slow%20down%20climate%20change%20and%20other%20ecocide%2C%20it%20seems%20most%20useful%20to%20first%20orient%20ourselves%20toward%20a%20broadly%20conceived%20vision%20of%20a%20more%20equitable%20and%20less%20consumerist%20world.%20We%20might%20then%20try%20to%20align%20our%20actions%20with%20helping%20to%20create%20that%20world%20in%20place%20of%20this%20one%2C%20piece%20by%20piece%2C%20even%20as%20conditions%20change%20significantly%20along%20the%20way%E2%80%94new%20problems%2C%20new%20possibilities%20opening%20before%20us%2C%20new%20conflicts%20and%20catastrophes%2C%20new%20understandings%20that%20change%20our%20older%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20here%20are%20some%20other%20good%20sources%20of%20information%20about%20the%20environment%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Findia%5C%22%3EDown%20to%20Earth%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mongabay.com%5C%22%3EMongabay%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%5C%22%3EIndiaSpend%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cseindia.org%5C%22%3ECenter%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20lesson%20I%20feel%20sure%20about%20is%20that%20any%20helpful%20response%20cannot%20entail%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fof-mice-and-men-energy-and-cancer%5C%22%3Epromoting%20the%20further%20expansion%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20human%20enterprise.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20found%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20using%20more%20energy%20and%20creating%20additional%20layers%20of%20technological%20or%20social%20complexity%20devised%20to%20maintain%20the%20course%20of%20our%20present%20civilisation.%20Rather%20we%20must%20look%20toward%20%3Cem%3Edisentangling%3C%2Fem%3E%20our