vices%20that%20benefit%20everyone%2C%20so%20everyone%20has%20enough.%20It%20also%20means%20those%20with%20more%20than%20they%20need%20should%20get%20used%20to%20having%20less%20kept%20exclusively%20to%20themselves%2C%20but%20rather%20learn%20to%20embrace%20a%20spirit%20of%20resource%20sharing.%20Being%20aware%20of%20how%20we%20use%20resources%20can%20change%20us.%20For%20example%2C%20reusing%20R%2FO%20wastewater%20for%20watering%20or%20washing%2C%20or%20recycling%20it%20back%20through%20our%20water%20storage%20systems%20can%20wake%20us%20up%20both%20to%20our%20profligacy%20and%20its%20pricelessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20mindful%20of%20your%20consumption%20habits%20versus%20your%20requirements%E2%80%94energy%2C%20water%2C%20gadgets%2C%20etc.%20We%20may%20laugh%20at%20people%20for%20avoiding%20plastic%20straws%20or%20bags%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20true%20that%20one%E2%80%99s%20individual%20actions%20won%E2%80%99t%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20plastic%20mountain.%20But%20their%20animating%20spirit%20can%20shift%20behavioural%20norms%20and%20snowball%20into%20larger%20social%20movements%20and%20political%20demands.%20Sometimes%20collective%20action%20can%20move%20mountains.%20Millions%20of%20individuals%20limiting%20use%20of%20simple%20things%20like%20plastic%20straws%20or%20bags%2C%20wherever%20possible%2C%20can%20add%20up%20to%20tons%20of%20less%20plastic%20killing%20turtles%20and%20seabirds%20or%20torturing%20the%20guts%20of%20urban%20cows%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20nothing.%20Keep%20the%20idea%20of%20ecological%20limits%20in%20mind%20and%20draw%20your%20own%20lines%20for%20your%20own%20behaviour%2C%20based%20on%20what%20makes%20sense%20to%20you.%20If%20nothing%20else%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20good%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20lucky%20enough%20to%20live%20in%20a%20city%20with%20a%20metro%20or%20other%20good%20public%20transit%20system%2C%20use%20it%20whenever%20you%E2%80%99re%20able.%20Limiting%20use%20of%20private%20vehicles%20redu