.%20Alternatively%2C%20help%20work%20on%20mitigating%20the%20harms%20of%20unavoidable%20megaprojects.%20In%20the%20decades%20to%20come%2C%20those%20who%20are%20less%20dependent%20on%20high%20energy%20and%20consumption%20lifestyles%20will%20also%20be%20better%20placed%20to%20deal%20with%20unpredictabilities%20in%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteer%20with%20environmental%20groups%20and%20communities%2C%20activists%20and%20providers%20of%20aid%2C%20strategists%20and%20workers.%20Multiple%20responses%20are%20required%2C%20which%20include%20working%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20blame%20yourself%20or%20others%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReducing%20our%20complex%20global%20crisis%2C%20born%20of%20very%20deep%20cultural%20roots%2C%20to%20finger-pointing%20based%20on%20facile%20reasonings%20will%20not%20begin%20to%20help%20anyone.%20Least%20of%20all%2C%20yourself.%20While%20we%20can%20hold%20people%20accountable%20for%20their%20decisions%2C%20it%20also%20helps%20to%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20our%20global%20predicament%20is%20not%20created%20by%20any%20one%20generation%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20nation%2C%20family%2C%20or%20person.%20Every%20one%20of%20us%20sits%20atop%20multilayered%20histories%20that%20inform%20our%20perceptions%20of%20the%20world%20and%20define%20our%20options%20within%20it.%20No%20one%20has%20the%20sole%20power%20to%20fix%20the%20past%20or%20the%20present.%20Everything%20is%20more%20complicated%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20expect%20%E2%80%98purity%E2%80%99%20of%20thought%20or%20action%20from%20yourself%20or%20anyone%20else%20who%20cares%20about%20the%20environment.%20Every%20one%20of%20us%20abounds%20in%20contradictions.%20None%20of%20us%20has%20perfect%20will%20or%20judgment%20or%20knowledge%20or%20even%20freedom%20of%20action%20in%20every%20sphere%20of%20our%20lives.%20We%20all%20do%20things%20that%20someone%20else%20will%20judge%20as%20hypocritical.%20Remember%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20all%20fighting%20different%20battles%20too.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20shame%20others%20for%20not%20doing%20exactly%20as%20you%E2%80%99re%20able%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccept%20that%20nothing%20you%20do%20will%20be%20enough.%20You%20alone%20cannot%20stop%20global%20warming%20or%20save%20the%20world.%20Nor%20is%20the%20goal%20to%20prove%20yourself%20an%20individual%20environmental%20hero.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20participate%20in%20local%20and%20global%20changes%20collectively%20driving%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20toward%20a%20more%20equitable%20and%20sustainable%20human%20enterprise.%20Like%20everyone%20else%2C%20you%20can%20only%20do%20your%20best%3B%20some%20days%20and%20some%20choices%20will%20be%20much%20harder%20than%20others.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20others%20shame%20you%20into%20doing%20less%20or%20more%20than%20you%E2%80%99re%20able%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20dream%20of%20utopias.%20Human%20beings%20aren%E2%80%99t%20capable%20of%20creating%20utopias.%20Such%20fantasies%20are%20anti-human%20and%20have%20often%20proven%20dangerous%20to%20attempt.%20But%20as%20individuals%2C%20as%20societies%2C%20as%20a%20species%2C%20we%20can%20certainly%20acknowledge%20that%20there%20have%20been%20times%20and%20places%20when%20we%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20more%20harmoniously%20and%20carefully.%20There%20are%20also%20times%20when%20we%20annihilate%20other%20people%20or%20species%20thoughtlessly%20or%20even%20fanatically.%20All%20these%20capacities%20are%20within%20us.%20Yet%20we%20can%20play%20our%20part%20in%20moving%20society%20toward%20its%20better%20self.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20us%20will%20at%20best%20be%20part%20of%20a%20changing%20tide%2C%20in%20our%20own%20way%2C%20for%20massive%20changes%20that%20will%20take%20years%20or%20generations%20to%20become%20fully%20established%E2%80%94if%20we%E2%80%99re%20lucky.%20And%20if%20we%E2%80%99re%20successful%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20find%20our%20way%20toward%20envisioning%20alternative%20futur