%20is%20also%20home%20to%20a%20diverse%20fauna%2C%20including%20leopards%2C%20wild%20buffaloes%2C%20tigers%2C%20hyenas%2C%20elephants%2C%20bears%2C%20pangolins%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20the%20tiger%20reserve%2C%20Jain%20observed%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20of%20wildlife%20and%20forest%20conservation%20among%20the%20local%20people.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20area%20is%20Naxal-affected%2C%20forest%20officials%20would%20fear%20going%20for%20patrolling.%20This%20patrolling%20gap%20led%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F203827%2Fifs-hero-india-woman-forest-encroach-jungle-mafia-forests-real-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erise%20in%20encroachment%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20poaching%20cases.%20People%20would%20cut%20down%20trees%20to%20build%20their%20establishments%20in%20animal%20habitats%20while%20poachers%20fanned%20the%20illegal%20wildlife%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jain%20informs%20that%20after%202008%2C%20the%20forest%20cover%20reduced%20from%20400%20trees%20per%20hectare%20to%2040%20trees%20per%20hectare.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345150%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJain%20informs%20that%20after%202008%2C%20the%20forest%20cover%20reduced%20from%20400%20trees%20per%20hectare%20to%2040%20trees%20per%20hectare.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20irresponsible%20behaviour%20was%20not%20new%2C%20he%20adds.%20Jain%20points%20out%20that%20during%20the%20British%20Raj%20and%20the%20Zamindari%20period%20after%20Independence%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246877%2Fsaving-tiger-india-reserve-chhattisgarh-jharkhand-wildlife-trust-of-india-udanti-sitanadi-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUdanti-Sitanadi%20tiger%20reserve%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20used%20as%20a%20game%20reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20anyone%20could%20shoot%20animals%20after%20paying%20a%20small%20fee.%20For%20instance%2C%20you%20could%20shoot%20a%20tiger%20paying%20Rs%2025%2C%20and%20wild%20buffalo%2C%20which%20is%20the%20state%20animal%2C%20with%20Rs%20100.%20This%20continued%20till%201972%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20have%20such%20low%20numbers%20of%20tigers.%20Currently%2C%20we%20have%20just%20one%20tiger.%20This%20makes%20our%20tiger%20reserve%20different%20from%20the%20Kanha%2C%20Ranthambore%2C%20or%20Pilibhit%20tiger%20reserves.%20Because%20of%20the%20encroachment%2C%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20progress%20eco-tourism%20in%20the%20region.%20Just%20a%20year%20back%2C%20we%20did%20not%20even%20have%20any%20gypsy%20safaris%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20evicting%20encroachers%20to%20welcoming%20wildlife%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20field%20visits%20to%20the%20forest%2C%20Jain%20would%20often%20see%20large%20charred%20spots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20out%20that%20giant%20100-year-old%20trees%20were%20burnt%20down%20to%20make%20huts%20and%20farmland.%20Immediately%2C%20I%20procured%20ISRO%20images%20from%202008%2C%202010%2C%20and%202012%2C%20and%20then%2C%20I%20conducted%20surveys%20using%20drones%20to%20assess%20the%20encroachment.%20After%20comparing%20both%20the%20images%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20the%20reserve%20was%20a%20dense%20forest%20until%202008.%20Now%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20an%20open%20forest%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20was%20enacted%20and%20it%20stated%20that%20any%20member%20or%20community%20that%20primarily%20resided%20in%20forest%20land%20for%20bona%20fide%20livelihood%20needs%20before%2013%20December%2C%202005%2C%20would%20be%20entitled%20to%20forest%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20the%20ISRO%20images%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20these%20people%20settled%20here%20after%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jain%20shares%20200%20encroachers%20were%20evicted%20and%20at%20least%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land%20was%20recovered%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb