20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20the%20State%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20High%20Court%20against%20the%20Forest%20Department.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20judgement%20was%20passed%20in%20our%20favour%20as%20we%20had%20all%20the%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20dated%2020%20June%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20writ%20petition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cencroachers%E2%80%9D%20and%20mentioned%20that%20the%20respondents%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20to%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rules%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20the%20help%20of%20forest%20guards%2C%20Jain%20was%20able%20to%20recover%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345152%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20forest%20guards%2C%20Jain%20was%20able%20to%20recover%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20order%20dated%2012%20December%2C%202023%2C%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Department%20mentioned%20that%20with%20ISRO%20images%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20the%20forest%20land%20was%20encroached%20after%202005%20and%20the%20documentation%20of%20petitioners%20does%20not%20support%20their%20claims%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20informs%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176709%2Fifs-civil-servant-hero-sikkim-nrega-sandeep-tambe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20official%20%3C%2Fa%3Econducted%20the%20first%20eviction%20proceeding%20in%20January%202023.%20And%20so%20far%2C%20at%20least%20600%20acres%20of%20forest%20land%20have%20been%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20build%20trust%20among%20other%20local%20villagers%20who%20have%20now%20become%20our%20sources%20for%20sharing%20information%20on%20poaching-related%20incidences.%20Within%20nine%20months%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20conduct%2032%20operations%20where%20we%20arrested%20134%20poachers%20and%20smugglers.%20With%20reduced%20poaching%20and%20encroachment%20cases%2C%20we%20believe%20tigers%20from%20neighbouring%20states%20will%20find%20safe%20shelter%20and%20repopulate%20the%20reserve%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20this%20work%20has%20also%20brought%20immense%20contentment%20to%20Jain.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20becoming%20an%20IFS%20officer%2C%20I%20wished%20to%20join%20the%20Delhi%20police%20force%20but%20I%20missed%20it%20by%20seven%20marks.%20This%20project%20made%20me%20do%20similar%20investigation%20work%20%E2%80%94%20from%20using%20the%20cyber%20cell%20to%20tracking%20call%20records%20and%20encroaching%20activities.%20I%20do%20not%20regret%20my%20decision%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20an%20official%20uniform%20has%20been%20given%20to%20only%20three%20units%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20police%2C%20and%20the%20forest%20officials.%20The%20purpose%20of%20this%20uniform%20is%20to%20provide%20protection.%20It%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20protect%20our%20natural%20heritage.%20Anyone%20can%20plant%20trees.%20But%20as%20a%20forest%20official%2C%20if%20we%20cannot%20save%20a%20tree%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20new%20afforestation%20drives%3F%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20IFS%20Varun%20Jain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fvillagers-attack-forest-personnel-clearing-encroachments-in-chhattisgarh-tiger-reserve-three-hurt%2Fcid%2F1941725%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVillagers%20attack%20forest%20personnel%20clearing%20encroachments%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20tiger%20reserve%3B%20three%20hurt%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20in%20The%20Telegraph%20online%20on%202%20June%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2FUsers%2FShivani%2520Gupta%2FDownloads%2FHIGH%2520COURT%2520OF%2520CHHATTISGARH%2520AT%2520BILASPUR%2520-%2520display_pdf.php.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHIGH%20COURT%20OF%20CHHATTISGARH%20AT%20BILASPUR%20Writ%20Petition%20(C)%20No.2700%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2FUsers%2FShivani%2520Gupta%2FDownloads%2F_Adesh_13_12_2023%2520(1).pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Chhattisgarh%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Department%20order%20dated%2012%20December%202023%3C%2