a.com%2F%3Fp%3D345065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreya%20Sharma%20started%20'Rest%20The%20Case'%20in%202021%2C%20a%20legal%20aggregator%20platform%20that%20provides%20a%20list%20of%201%2C200%20specialised%20lawyers%20across%20200%20cities%20in%20India.%20It%20also%20provides%20basic%20legal%20templates%20like%20rent%20agreements%20and%20explains%20legal%20terms%20that%20everyone%20should%20know.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345065%2Fhow-to-find-a-lawyer-legal-startup-pune-shreya-sharma-divorce-family-court-business-property-law-rent-agreement%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Grow%20Raspberries%2C%20Blueberries%20in%20India%3F%20Woman%20Uses%20Low-Cost%20Innovation%20to%20Run%20Berry%20Biz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20tonnes%20of%20exotic%20fruits%20including%20blueberries%20and%20raspberries%20are%20imported%20for%20urban%20Indian%20consumers%20owing%20to%20their%20wide%20range%20of%20health%20benefits.%20Data%20shows%20that%20raspberry%2C%20blackberry%2C%20blueberry%2C%20and%20cranberry%20imports%20into%20India%20skyrocketed%20to%20870%20tonnes%20in%202022%20%E2%80%93%20indicating%20a%20surge%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indexbox.io%2Fsearch%2Fprice-for-raspberry-blackberry-blueberry-and-cranberry-india%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25202022%252C%2520raspberry%252C%2520blackberry%252C%2C616%2525%2520against%2520the%2520previous%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E148%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20to%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20Highbush%20Blueberry%20Council%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fdemand-for-us-blueberry-rising-in-india%2Farticle34852525.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank