r%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F140950%2Findian-scientists-develop-sensor-for-early-detection-of-chronic-kidney-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronic%20kidney%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20advised%20dialysis%20twice%20a%20week.%20As%20this%20treatment%20was%20not%20available%20near%20her%20residence%2C%20she%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20Dehradun%20and%20stay%20there%20for%20two%20nights%20every%20week%20to%20get%20the%20dialysis%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20single%20mother%2C%20being%20separated%20from%20her%20son%2C%20spending%20on%20travel%2C%20and%20eight%20nights%20at%20lodging%20every%20month%2C%20was%20much%20more%20than%20what%20she%20could%20afford%2C%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20faced%20by%20the%20ASHA%20worker%20resonates%20with%20many%20residing%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobal%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20(GBD)%202015%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chronic%20Kidney%20Disease%20(CKD)%20ranks%20as%20the%20eighth%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20India%2C%20largely%20because%20many%20patients%20develop%20complications%20leading%20to%20end-stage%20renal%20disease.%20A%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E%20estimated%20that%20two%20lakh%20people%20in%20India%20develop%20end-stage%20renal%20disease%20every%20year%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250227%2Fshashank-moddhia-mumbai-startup-renal-project-affordable-kidney-dialysis-in-india-healthcare-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20long-term%20dialysis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20costs%20associated%20with%20dialysis%20care%20add%20to%20the%20financial%20woes%20of%20patients.%20Collaborating%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Government%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20identified%20renal%20care%20as%20a%20major%20g